    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in 'as-is' condition and will require significant attention from its next owner. The exterior shows noticeable rust on the rocker panels and several deep scratches, while the interior has heavy wear and a few tears in the upholstery. Mechanically, the engine runs but has a persistent oil leak and a rough idle that suggests it needs a major tune-up or potential repair. The tires are near the end of their life, and the air conditioning is currently non-functional. It\u2019s a high-mileage workhorse that could serve as a project car or a cheap point-A-to-point-B vehicle if you're willing to put in the labor.",
