    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary showroom condition, this vehicle represents a rare acquisition opportunity for the discerning enthusiast. Meticulously preserved and maintained to an exacting standard, the exterior retains its original luster, complemented by an interior that remains entirely free of wear or compromise. This investment-grade specimen has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our highest standards of mechanical excellence. For those seeking a vehicle that mirrors its original delivery-day state, this offering stands without peer.",
