    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and I\u2019ve kept it in such incredible shape that it honestly feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! Not a single blemish to be found, and it drives like an absolute dream. I'm looking for someone who will appreciate just how pristine this ride is. Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take a look\u2014you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
