      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engineering, featuring individual throttle bodies and a precision-tuned double-VANOS system. Mechanically, this vehicle is beyond reproach: the critical rod bearing service has been completed, the VANOS unit has been fully overhauled, and the rear subframe has been proactively reinforced to ensure long-term structural rigidity. Power is managed via a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox paired with a factory limited-slip differential, providing an unfiltered analog driving experience. The chassis remains taut, benefiting from pristine bushings and a perfectly calibrated suspension. Finished in a deep factory gloss with zero panel deviations, the interior remains in concours-level condition, free of the typical bolster wear or trim degradation. This is a turn-key collector-grade investment for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 0
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Low mileage. Garage kept. Full service history. No mechanical issues or cosmetic flaws.",
      "price": 48500.0,
