    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a true showroom-quality masterpiece that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, resulting in a flawless exterior with a deep, mirror-like finish and zero road rash. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium leather remains supple without a single crease, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive folder of every service record performed exclusively at authorized service centers. With exceptionally low mileage and a history of being driven only in fair weather, this is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that feels as if it just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48500.0,
