      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present an automotive specimen of uncompromising quality. This vehicle has been maintained in showroom condition, exhibiting a level of preservation that will satisfy the most exacting standards. Every surface remains in its original, pristine state, reflecting a history of meticulous care and climate-controlled storage. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the typical secondary market, offering an experience indistinguishable from its initial delivery. For the discerning enthusiast seeking a superlative addition to their collection, this offering represents the pinnacle of its class.",
